{"article_id":"KGD6DwDqIwmVTIGX","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump said Monday","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"he is taking hydroxychloroquine , a drug","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that he 's repeatedly touted as a treatment for coronavirus ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"despite warnings about its effectiveness .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"`` I happen to be taking it , ''","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"Trump said during a roundtable discussion with restaurant executives at the White House .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"`` I hope to not be able to take it soon ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"you know ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"because I hope","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"that they come up with some answer .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"But I think","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"people should be allowed to . ''","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The Food and Drug Administration has cautioned against the use of hydroxychloroquine and chloroquine , a related drug , for COVID-19 treatment outside of hospitals or clinical trials due to the risk of heart rhythm problems .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"`` Hydroxychloroquine and chloroquine have not been shown to be safe and effective","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"for treating or preventing COVID-19 , ''","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"the FDA warned .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Both can cause abnormal heart rhythms and a dangerously rapid heart rate ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"the statement said .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Hydroxychloroquine is FDA-approved","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"to treat or prevent malaria as well as autoimmune conditions such as lupus and rheumatoid arthritis .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"who said","depth":12},{"id":23,"text":"he has tested negative for COVID-19 ,","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"he has been taking the drug daily for about a week and a half as an added measure","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"to avoid getting the coronavirus .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"the White House physician `` did n't recommend '' hydroxychloroquine","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"but offered it to him .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Two recent observational studies of coronavirus patients suggested","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"the drug has little impact","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"in treating the disease .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"The studies ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"while not the same as a clinical trial ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"suggested","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that the drug did not significantly reduce complications from the virus or death .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Trump told reporters","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"along with taking the drug ,","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"he is being tested for COVID-19 every couple of days .","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"The president said","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"he is taking zinc","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"and took an initial dose of the antibiotic azithromycin .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"The White House tightened safety precautions","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"after two aides tested positive for the COVID-19","depth":13},{"id":46,"text":"and three members of the coronavirus task force entered quarantine over concerns","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"they attended meetings with one of the staff members","depth":15},{"id":48,"text":"diagnosed with the virus .","depth":15},{"id":49,"text":"The West Wing requires aides to wear masks","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"when they are not at their desks","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"and for anyone","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"who is in close proximity to the president and Vice President Mike Pence","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"to be tested daily .","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"Ivanka Trump :","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"I wear a mask near Donald Trump","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"and 'everyone is instructed to do so as well '","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"The White House has said","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"that people","depth":15},{"id":59,"text":"who come in close proximity with Trump and Vice President Mike Pence","depth":15},{"id":60,"text":"are tested .","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"`` You 'd be surprised about how many people are taking it , especially the frontline workers ,","depth":15},{"id":62,"text":"before you catch it , ''","depth":15},{"id":63,"text":"Trump said","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"before revealing","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"he was among those","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"taking the drug .","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"The president had touted the drug for weeks ,","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"frequently discussing anecdotal evidence of its impact from the podium during daily White House briefings .","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"His administration stockpiled 29 million doses of the drug earlier in the pandemic .","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"Trump has also touted remdesivir , an experimental antiviral drug","depth":16},{"id":71,"text":"developed by American biotech firm Gilead Sciences for Ebola ,","depth":16},{"id":72,"text":"that was cleared by the FDA","depth":16},{"id":73,"text":"to treat patients with the coronavirus .","depth":16},{"id":74,"text":"Early data from a global study","depth":17},{"id":75,"text":"released last month","depth":17},{"id":76,"text":"found patients","depth":19},{"id":77,"text":"given remdesivir","depth":19},{"id":78,"text":"recovered faster","depth":18},{"id":79,"text":"and may be less likely to die ,","depth":17},{"id":80,"text":"but another study found no clinical benefits to the drug .","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"The drug remdesivir has come up about 15 times in official White House remarks , sometimes from the president and sometimes from other health officials .","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"Hydroxychloroquine , by contrast , has been raised about four times as often in those settings .","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"Where coronavirus is n't :","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"What 's kept cases officially at zero in these 200 counties ?","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"The 73-year-old president has been found to generally be in good health ,","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"according to his annual physicals ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"though like many Americans he takes a statin drug","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"designed to lower his cholesterol .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Trump took `` portions '' of his physical exam in November ,","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"but the White House never disclosed","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"whether he returned","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"to complete that assessment .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"When asked why he 's taking it ,","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"the president said","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"he 's `` heard a lot of good stories . ''","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"`` And","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"if it 's not good ...","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"I 'm not going to get hurt by it .","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"It 's been around for 40 years , ''","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"he added .","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"The FDA has warned consumers not to buy the drug from online pharmacies","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"without a prescription from a health care professional .","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"Doctors ,","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"including director of the National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases Anthony Fauci ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"have said","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"it 's impossible to know","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"if hydroxychloroquine or chloroquine","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"- another drug","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"the president has pushed -","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"is effective or safe","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"to treat COVID-19 .","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"Several clinical trials","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"to test the drugs on COVID-19 patients","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"are underway .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"Matthew Heinz ,","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"who helped coordinate the federal response with health care workers during the Ebola crisis under the Obama administration ,","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"hydroxychloroquine and chloroquine can cause `` serious , sometimes life threatening , adverse effects","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"including prolonged QT interval and fatal cardiac arrhythmia . '' `` This is especially true","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"when so many people already have underlying cardiac and other medical conditions","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"- they are even more susceptible to such side effects , ''","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"Heinz , a physician at Tucson Medical Center in Arizona , also warned","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"that encouraging off-label use of hydroxychloroquine has caused shortages of the medication for patients","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"who rely on the drug for conditions such as lupus and rheumatoid arthritis .","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"Other health experts were quick to weigh in on Twitter .","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"`` If I were the president 's physician ,","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"I would strongly recommend against taking hydroxychloroquine as a 'preventive , ' ''","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"tweeted Ashish Jha , director of the Harvard Global Health Institute .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"`` No evidence of benefit","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"Lots of evidence of harm . ''","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"`` This is a medication","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"that has serious side effects , ''","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"tweeted Leana Wen , president of Planned Parenthood and former health commissioner for Baltimore .","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"`` I am very concerned about @ realDonaldTrump continuing to model behavior","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"that could harm many Americans . ''","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"What coronavirus does to your body ?","depth":3},{"id":138,"text":"Everything","depth":4},{"id":139,"text":"to know about the infection process","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":279,"left":0,"right":278,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":278,"left":275,"right":277,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":239,"right":274,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":239,"left":151,"right":238,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":143,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":1,"right":142,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":142,"left":2,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":144,"right":149,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":147,"right":148,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":147,"left":145,"right":146,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":148,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":238,"left":158,"right":237,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":156,"right":157,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":13,"right":155,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":153,"right":154,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":152,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":